data.description: Welcome to your new home, a sanctuary with no backyard neighbors and devoid of carpeting! As you step through the front door, the living room with a cozy fireplace greets you on the right, while the dining room beckons on the left. Continuing on to the kitchen, you'll discover the eat-in area and a convenient pantry. The kitchen seamlessly leads to the laundry room, which connects to the garage. Near the staircase, a half bath and coat closet offer practicality. Upstairs, your new abode unfolds with two guest rooms, a guest bathroom, and a bonus room that's ready for your personal touch. The primary bedroom boasts a trey ceiling, dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. A french door leads to the back patio and a generously sized yard. This outdoor oasis includes a smart sprinkler system with rain sensors to prevent overwatering your lawn. Don't miss the chance to turn this house into your cherished new home! Schedule a showing today.
